description.content:
Introduction:


I'm a Senior Web Developer with almost 8+ years of experience in web design and development. I can develop custom website as per your need and business requirements.


Services Offer:


I will develop sites like:

  1. Landing pages
  2. Management systems
  3. Portfolio
  4. Product-related site
  5. Content Management System
  6. School Management System
  7. Social Media Site
  8. Chatting sites
  9. Online Quiz Management System
  10. Custom Site according to your requirements


Why Choose me:


  • Best Rates -- Excellent Quality
  • Unlimited Revisions
  • Consultation Services To discuss before start
  • All discussion through meetings so that understand your requirements easily
  • All IT-Based solutions under one user.


Pre-Requisites Required:


  • Detailed discussion before placing the order.
  • All discussions and help to proceed in a right direction


Other Services:


  1. WordPress Web (https://www.fiverr.com/shahrukhijaz597/create-landing-page-with-elementor-pro)
  2. Shopify Web (https://www.fiverr.com/shahrukhijaz597/build-shopify-dropshipping-store-or-ecommerce-website)
  3. Web Scraping (https://www.fiverr.com/shahrukhijaz597/create-flask-website-and-rest-api)



Contact me Before Placing Order To discuss all details


Best Regar

questionsAndAnswers.question: Website will be mobile responsive?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, All pages will be mobile responsive

questionsAndAnswers.question: What I need to send you for starting website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I need detailed description of task, Website images and content and a structure diagram for the complete flow or simply a zoom meeting will work!

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer custom website services?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can develop a custom website for you.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Deliver will based on website file or you will upload to git/hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I can do as you want to upload on git/upload to hosting/deliver website files.

reviews.comment: Great development, He stick to my expectations of not getting something canned using wordpress or vix or similar. For now we just needed a simple static experience and that's what he delivered, so thank you for that. This will help us in our I+D for improving our development strategies.

We could not be more happy with the delivered work. It really helped that we were able to work flexibly time-wise, and whenever we were in need of help, he was right there. The initial phone call really helped as I could tell there was attention to detail but it did exceed my expectations!

Working with Spiderhunts was a great experience. He completed the work ahead of schedule, very patiently made revisions until the website was to my 100% satisfaction, and he communicated daily with updates. His coding expertise is exceptional and I really appreciated that he took pride in making sure his client is satisfied with the completed project. He was never rude about revisions. Great work! Will use again for sure!

seller_response.comment: Thank you so much for your brief honest review :)

reviews.comment: Im very happy with the results! He really pays attention to detail and truly listened to what I wanted. The final website is exactly what I envisioned. He was patient with me throughout the process. I changed my mind on a few things along the way, and he handled it with professionalism and understanding, ensuring every adjustment was made exactly as I wanted. He was easy to work with, communicated clearly, and made the entire experience stress-free. Thank you for bringing my vision to life!

This is first milestone of large project. I am closely working with Shahrukh and his attention to details , commitment is commendable. Looking forward to build something great together with Shahrukh and his team. Bravo !
